commit message: Device: Add an ability to check for the LG manufacturer

AppWidget: Avoid of a bug in AppWidgetPickActivity that causes NPE

This avoids a bug in the com.android.settings.AppWidgetPickActivity,
which is used to select widgets. This just adds empty extras to the
intent, avoiding the bug. See more:
http://code.google.com/p/android/issues/detail?id=4272
